title: SF9 Surprises Fans With Dance Practice Video Of “Still My Lady” On White Day
text:
Shares 263   
SF9 is back with another dance practice video and, this time, the video is a full version of their choreography for “Still My Lady.” 
As the video was released on March 14, a day that some countries celebrate as White Day, the video seems to be SF9’s White Day gift to fans. The members are also all wearing white shirts presumably to commemorate the holiday. 
Meanwhile, SF9 released a Chinese version of their mini-album “Burning Sensation” and also shared a dance practice video for their title track “Roar” last month.
